睇就好"},{"pid":"d5cef4ec95cdb820fa970061b2b256b8f10f082e","tid":616593,"uid":63843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T11:15:27.000Z","msg":"可以自己寫下文<br />\n乜都好 日記又好 評論又好 唔一定要發佈<br />\n一邊寫一邊改善自己既表達能力 最緊要自己接受到<br />\n<br />\n其實簡簡單單執好D病句用字已經好夠<br />\n唔一定要用深既詞匯"},{"pid":"dd4b9cbdee68b22f35e4a4639611e2abce6f83cb","tid":616593,"uid":81424,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T11:17:13.000Z","msg":"忌用 的地得我你他們您化式性了<br />\n忌用 被動句<br />\n凡能用動詞者皆用動詞 即<br />\n某人作出演講 -&gt; 某人演講<br />\n分清褒貶 <br />\n如「被」、「遭」 為貶 <br />\n「受」、「獲」為中立而近乎褒<br />\n<br />\n咁上下"},{"pid":"acb2105b302147235b5ca64c2f31decb011fb5f3","tid":616593,"uid":65897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T11:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇大陸d原創小説，一d口啤好嘅作家同岀名嘅小説d文筆真係好好，又唔悶</blockquote>睇簡體好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n有d網有繁體"},{"pid":"1bbd5c47e76f71192e3b273b53823a9b345ede4a","tid":616593,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T11:24:31.000Z","msg":"其實睇古典文學會係好選擇<br />\n有興趣可以起我底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過「好」中文嘅定義，要視情況<br />\n唔見得始終活嘅語言係具有彈性"},{"pid":"ebaedbb0e1e27ad2ad1aa0c852124f0cb98552c5","tid":616593,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4dc353d7aad838f8de115b6c22e2be3dd8e998fb","tid":616593,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d372cc6369e36036ea51ed7190edce87de2d8c","tid":616593,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dbefd2c542bf5b010daf5d32b56a9a470fec59fc","tid":616593,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:47:42.000Z","msg":"如何避免歐式及中共式中文?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T11:03:06.000Z","msg":"根本冇人care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T11:08:52.000Z","msg":"咁依加商業上係點睇中文 ? 叻英文就夠?"},"citedBy":0,"reply